params._amount: amount of stable coins sent by buyer

calcRPBFromPercentage(uint256).details: get Tranche A exchange rate (tokens with 18 decimals)

claimAaveRewards(address,uint256).details: claim token rewards from all assets in protocol and transfer them to fees collector

params._amount: amount of rewards token to claim (set it to 0 if you want to claim for all tokens)

getAaveReserveData(uint256).details: get Aave reserve Data for an asset liquidityRate is the return percentage for that asset (multiply by 10^27)

getDataProvider().details: get Aave Pool Address Provider starting from lending pool address provider

getEthBalance().details: get eth balance on this contract

getTokenBalance(address).details: get every token balance in this contract

getTotalValue(uint256).details: get Tranche total value in underlying tokens

returns._0: tranche total value in underlying tokens

getTrAValue(uint256).details: get Tranche A value in underlying tokens

returns.trANormValue: tranche A value in underlying tokens

getTrBValue(uint256).details: get Tranche B value in underlying tokens

returns._0: tranche B value in underlying tokens

getTrancheACurrentRPB(uint256).details: get RPB for a given percentage (expressed in 1e18)

params._newAmount: new amount entering tranche B (underlying token decimals)

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

params._amount: amount of stable coins sent by buyer
amount of stable coins sent by buyer

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

params._addressProviderContract: aave lending pool address provider contract address (kovan: 0x88757f2f99175387aB4C6a4b3067c77A695b0349)

setBlocksPerYear(uint256).details: set how many blocks will be produced per year on the blockchain

setDecimals(uint256,uint8).details: check if a cToken is allowed or not

setNewEnvironment(address,address,addres.details: set new addresses for price oracle, fees collector and tranche deployer

setTrancheAFixedPercentage(uint256,uint2.details: set tranche redemption percentage scaled by 1e18

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

transferTokenToFeesCollector(address,uin.details: transfer tokens in this contract to fees collector contract

withdrawEthToFeesCollector(uint256).details: transfer ethers in this contract to fees collector contract
